column5: I have the chance to get out for the rest of the day and fish Simcoe in my boat , Any one care to join up for the day . Perch & Bass ...........................................
Why don't you just get up and go? You'll lose another 3 hours of fishing time just waiting for someone to show up.
Your right Roy , times a wasting , i'll be gone once am sign out .
Still a nice gesture Ron!,but youse a wastin time lol.

Coming of the lake a short while ago as i turned to come in Kempenfelt  . With my haul and fish in hand , i waltz her right down the bay , water was a bit choppy but none the less it was a great day to be fish'in . Now she's time to make some fillets .
Nice fish and nice sunset pic
Nice pics Ron.Good to see ya enjoying the summers wind down.
Fillets are put away , can't wait for dinner tomorow night .. lol , thanks for the good comments there folks , tight lines til the next time .

I have a cottage on fox island...and have yet to target in on ANY fish. Here right now and frying frustrated wasting gas haha  Help a brother out  Nice pics by the way! Time to go cut down a big tree that went down on labour day.....
I PUSHED THE WRONG BUTTON AGAIN ......
If your on Fox , you must have seen me last night trolling around the island , i was the only boat out there ,  you might want to send me a PM .......LOL
